snippet.title: Worshippers of Cthulhu Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
A new trailer for Worshippers of Cthulhu provided an overview of the gameplay in this eldritch cult simulator. Burn sacrifices and mark citizens to satisfy Cthulu when it launches on October 21, 2024. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS
